original_title: The Croc That Ate Jaws: Ancient Enemies
overview: Around the world, crocs and gators are moving out to sea and deep into shark territory. With reports of clashes on the rise, scientists are sending cameras to investigate what happens when two of the deadliest predators on the planet match bites! Biologist and host Mike Heithaus investigates whether these predators are facing off more often than we realize and who comes out on top when they do.
title: The Croc That Ate Jaws: Ancient Enemies
